    "# 教程 07：小数据预测与优化 — GPR + 贝叶斯优化\n",
    "\n",
    "**学习目标** ⭐\n",
    "- 理解高斯过程回归 (GPR) 的原理\n",
    "- 使用本仓库的 GPR 参考实现进行回归预测\n",
    "- 学习贝叶斯优化 (BO) 的核心流程\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "theory",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 高斯过程回归简介\n",
    "\n",
    "高斯过程 (GP) 是一种非参数概率模型，在**小数据场景**下具有显著优势：\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **预测不确定性**：不仅给出预测均值，还给出置信区间\n",
    "2. **核函数灵活性**：通过 RBF、Matern 等核函数编码先验知识\n",
    "3. **数据效率高**：在小样本下表现优于深度神经网络\n",
    "\n",
    "### 核心公式\n",
    "\n",
    "GP 假设 $f(x) \\sim GP(m(x), k(x, x'))$，给定观测数据后的预测分布：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\mu_* = K_*^T (K + \\sigma^2 I)^{-1} y$$\n\n",
    "$$\\Sigma_* = K_{**} - K_*^T (K + \\sigma^2 I)^{-1} K_*$$\n\n",
    "其中 $K_{ij} = k(x_i, x_j)$ 是核函数矩阵。\n\n",
    "## 贝叶斯优化\n",
    "\n",
    "贝叶斯优化 (BO) 用于黑箱函数的全局优化，核心是 GP 替代模型 + 采集函数：\n",
    "- **EI** (Expected Improvement)：期望改进量\n",
    "- **UCB** (Upper Confidence Bound)：上置信界\n",
    "- **PI** (Probability of Improvement)：改进概率"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "import_gpr",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys, os\n",
    "repo_root = os.path.abspath(os.path.join(os.getcwd(), '..'))\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, repo_root)\n",
    "\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    from prediction.SmallData.kernels import RBFKernel, MaternKernel, SumKernel\n",
    "    from prediction.SmallData.gpr import (\n",
    "        GaussianProcessRegressor,\n",
    "        ExpectedImprovement,\n",
    "        BayesianOptimizer,\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    import torch\n",
    "    import numpy as np\n",
    "    print(\"GPR 模块加载成功 ✅\")\n",
    "except ImportError as e:\n",
    "    print(f\"加载失败: {e}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "gp_example",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## GP 回归 — 从少量样本中学习\n",
    "\n",
    "用只有 10 个观测点来拟合一个非线性函数。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "gp_fit",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "true_fn = lambda x: np.sin(2 * np.pi * x) * np.exp(-x)\n",
    "\n",
    "n_train = 10\n",
    "x_train = np.sort(np.random.rand(n_train)).astype(np.float32).reshape(-1, 1)\n",
    "y_train = (true_fn(x_train.squeeze()) + np.random.randn(n_train) * 0.1).astype(np.float32)\n",
    "\n",
    "x_t = torch.from_numpy(x_train)\n",
    "y_t = torch.from_numpy(y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "kernel = RBFKernel(length_scale=0.3, variance=1.0)\n",
    "gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=kernel, noise_scale=0.05)\n",
    "gp.fit(x_t, y_t)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"训练点数: {n_train}\")\n",
    "print(f\"核参数: length_scale={kernel.length_scale.item():.3f}, variance={kernel.variance.item():.3f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "gp_predict",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x_test = torch.linspace(-0.5, 1.5, 200).unsqueeze(-1)\n",
    "mu, std = gp.predict(x_test, return_std=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "mu = mu.numpy()\n",
    "std = std.numpy()\n",
    "x_test_np = x_test.numpy()\n",
    "y_true = true_fn(x_test_np.squeeze())\n",
    "\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "    plt.fill_between(x_test_np.squeeze(), mu - 2*std, mu + 2*std,\n",
    "                     alpha=0.2, color='b', label='95% 置信区间')\n",
    "    plt.plot(x_test_np, y_true, 'k-', label='真实函数', linewidth=2)\n",
    "    plt.plot(x_test_np, mu, 'b--', label='GP 预测', linewidth=2)\n",
    "    plt.scatter(x_train, y_train, c='r', s=80, zorder=5, label='观测点')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('x')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('f(x)')\n",
    "    plt.title('高斯过程回归 — 10 个样本点学习非线性函数')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.grid(alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "    rmse = np.sqrt(np.mean((mu - y_true) ** 2))\n",
    "    print(f\"RMSE: {rmse:.4f}\")\n",
    "except ImportError:\n",
    "    print(\"需要 matplotlib\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bo_example",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 贝叶斯优化 — 寻找函数最大值\n",
    "\n",
    "用 GP 作为替代模型，通过 EI 采集函数高效搜索一维函数的全局最大值。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "bo_demo",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def objective(x):\n",
    "    \"\"\"带多个局部最优的目标函数\"\"\"\n",
    "    return -(x - 0.3) ** 2 * torch.sin(5 * torch.pi * x) + 1.0\n",
    "\n",
    "# 可视化目标函数\n",
    "x_plot = torch.linspace(0, 1, 200).unsqueeze(-1)\n",
    "y_plot = objective(x_plot)\n",
    "\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
    "    plt.plot(x_plot.numpy(), y_plot.numpy(), 'k-', label='目标函数', linewidth=2)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 执行 BO\n",
    "    bounds = np.array([[0.0, 1.0]])\n",
    "    gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=RBFKernel(length_scale=0.15, variance=1.0), noise_scale=0.01)\n",
    "    bo = BayesianOptimizer(gp, bounds, n_initial=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "    best_x, best_y = bo.maximize(objective, n_iter=15)\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 标记采样点和最优结果\n",
    "    x_obs = torch.stack(bo.x_observed)\n",
    "    y_obs = torch.stack(bo.y_observed)\n",
    "    plt.scatter(x_obs.numpy(), y_obs.numpy(), c='blue', s=50, alpha=0.6, label='采样点')\n",
    "    plt.scatter([best_x.item()], [best_y.item()], c='red', s=150, marker='*', label='最优解', zorder=5)\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('x')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('f(x)')\n",
    "    plt.title('贝叶斯优化 — 3 初始点 + 15 轮迭代')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.grid(alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f\"找到的最优解: x = {best_x.item():.4f}, f(x) = {best_y.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "except ImportError:\n",
    "    print(\"需要 matplotlib\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "optimize_gp",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## GP 超参数优化\n",
    "\n",
    "GPR 可以通过最大化对数边际似然自动学习最优的核参数。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "train_gp",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "kernel = RBFKernel(length_scale=1.0, variance=1.0)\n",
    "gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=kernel, noise_scale=0.1)\n",
    "optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(gp.parameters(), lr=1e-2)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"优化 GP 超参数...\")\n",
    "for epoch in range(100):\n",
    "    optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "    loss = gp.negative_log_marginal_likelihood(x_t, y_t)\n",
    "    loss.backward()\n",
    "    optimizer.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"优化结果:\")\n",
    "print(f\"  长度尺度 l = {kernel.length_scale.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f"  信号方差 σ² = {kernel.variance.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  噪声 σ_n = {gp.noise.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  对数边际似然 = {-loss.item():.4f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "summary",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 总结 📋\n",
